<subSubSection id="C364A2C5262DFFDCFF3FB489ACFDF7F2" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC1F14E262DFFDCFF3FB489ACFDF7F2" blockId="1.[136,1452,728,2051]" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFF3FB489A8D3F82F" bold="true" box="[189,389,1988,2014]" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">Taxonomic notes</emphasis>
:—Owing to colour of flower, presence of hairs at the base of lip 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E8ACD262DFFDCFBD9B488ADA1F82F" authorityName="Vuong, Aver. &amp; V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2022" box="[1115,1271,1988,2014]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="xuandangii">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFBD9B488ADA1F82F" box="[1115,1271,1988,2014]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">B. xuandangii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
looks similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E8ACD262DFFDCFF0AB4A4A87BF7F3" authorityName="J. F. Liu, S. R. Lan &amp; Y. C. Liang" authorityYear="2018" box="[136,301,2025,2050]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="yongtaiense">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFF0AB4A4A87BF7F3" box="[136,301,2025,2050]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">B. yongtaiense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E8ACD262DFFDCFEB9B4A4A8E5F7F3" authorityName="Vuong, Aver. &amp; V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2020" box="[315,435,2024,2050]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sridithii">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFEB9B4A4A8E5F7F3" box="[315,435,2024,2050]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">B. sridithii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C7E8ACD262DFFDCFE6BB4A4AB13F7F3" authorityName="Aver. &amp; Vuong" authorityYear="2019" box="[489,581,2024,2050]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="layae">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFE6BB4A4AB13F7F3" box="[489,581,2024,2050]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">B. layae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the morphological comparison of similar species is presented in the 
<tableCitation id="C6FCC4F5262DFFDCFACFB4A5ACF2F7F3" box="[1357,1444,2024,2050]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="3.[136,224,160,184]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="TABLE 1. Morphological comparison between B. xuandangii, B. yongtaiense, B. srithidii, B. layae." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/DF01A1C6262FFFDEFF0AB3EDADE3FF46" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" tableUuid="DF01A1C6262FFFDEFF0AB3EDADE3FF46">
<emphasis id="B90A2D5C262DFFDCFACFB4A5ACF2F7F3" bold="true" box="[1357,1444,2024,2050]" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">Table 1</emphasis>
</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
